<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你還記得<delay20 />今天是煙火大會嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大會從今晚7點開始，<delay20 /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要記得來喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />期待已久的煙火大會<delay20 />今晚7點就要開始囉！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可別忘了喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你喔，<delay20 />今晚7點舉辦的煙火大會，<delay20 />
你也會來嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一直很期待<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能和你一起看煙火呢！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會<delay8 />馬上就要開始囉。<delay frames="40" />
感覺好緊張喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經<delay20 />準備好了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不論是做什麼，做好心理準備都是很重要的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這也是為了讓自己能盡力去享受過程。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />畢竟是難得的煙火大會，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們就一起好好享受活動吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好了，今晚的天氣也很不錯呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣<delay8 />應該能好好欣賞
美麗的煙火吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今晚的夜空<delay8 />被煙火染上了各種顏色，<delay8 />
美到讓人忘記日常煩惱喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要回想起那景象，就覺得很感動呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的煙火<delay8 />真的很美啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我看煙火<delay20 />看得太入神，<delay8 />
都忘記要去補妝了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">雖然煙火大會已經結束了，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是像這樣暫時沉浸在美好的
餘韻中也不錯呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的煙火大會<delay20 />已經結束了呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不論是多麼歡樂的活動，
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一旦結束後總是會讓人感到落寞<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過你放心，沒事的。<delay frames="40" />
讓我們懷抱著至今為止的美好回憶，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從明天開始繼續努力吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00">雖然今年的煙火大會已經全部結束了，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我有盡情享受，所以沒有任何遺憾喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來可以<delay8 />好好期待明年的活動呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />今年的煙火大會<delay8 />玩得真開心呢！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是明年我還有機會看高空煙火，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到時會不會回憶起今年的活動呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>